  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "May 1995.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Morris, you were just saying that you had offer from Polish friends to hide.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes, but my-- they were saying my parents didn't want to go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we had to make a quick decision because it was really very bad.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We knew that the Germans will come any-- any time now.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we digged a very big hole in the garden there-- quite, quite big and with shrubs all around.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We put blankets there and food for about a week or so.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were hoping that the Germans will come, and after a day or so, whatever they will do, we be able to come back and see our parents.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But within the last minute, it didn't take long-- a day or so-- and the Germans came in, and we could hear shooting going on.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And our next-door neighbor came and told us, look, better get away because the Germans are already here, and most probably you can hear the shooting.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we went still with our parents to the hiding.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were there, my parents and one sister with them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one sister went-- because this sister had very good papers that she was working for the Germans, and we were sure they won't do anything to her.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's what's coming to, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we took our parents there, and you can imagine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we said goodbye to them, and we-- we run away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we run to this Pole-- the one who promised us that he keep us in case something will happen.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "On the way, we could see hundreds of people running everywhere, people that we knew from the city, and no one could do anything to help them.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we-- we arrived there, and he took us in, the Pole.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
